{"tid":1257312,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[626] 19國領事館馬拉松式請願 最新資訊","createTime":"2019-06-25T13:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T11:52:13.000Z","uid":10524,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f167c8d71374295abf80b2c7e45ee90a076da681","tid":1257312,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T13:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZngYdnK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZngYdnK.png&h=4e693d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WtN1a9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWtN1a9r.png&h=72dcb491&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rbxhPs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rbxhPs.png&h=e53e1c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/25/212106_432102ac484035e7258882a5e23195ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2F212106_432102ac484035e7258882a5e23195ec.png&h=5cdac3e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/25/212108_52f2439f966157d3ffb992a7f8eb5da0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2F212108_52f2439f966157d3ffb992a7f8eb5da0.png&h=63cb6f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/25/212111_f70da49ddc26fe945fb18e50867288b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2F212111_f70da49ddc26fe945fb18e50867288b4.png&h=2a558a90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地已經同警方協調好聽日既三條遊行路線。<br />\n<br />\n由於已經約好領事館請願時間，敬請手足準時上午九時到遮打花園會合。<br />\n<br />\n請穿著輕便黑色衣物，可配戴口罩。帶備足夠食水及乾糧，並攜帶雨具。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍將一同靜默遊行往美領、歐盟及英領，然後分成三隊前往其他領事館。手足可以預先考慮選擇的路線，屆時按照指示分批前行。預計所有路線會在下午四時前結束。"},{"pid":"bb9194331cfd80db468d919757b5f40cd31064cf","tid":1257312,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0